summary: Arsenal's Premier League title ambitions suffered a major blow as they fell to a disappointing 0-2 defeat against Aston Villa. Meanwhile, Bayern Munich and Arsenal played to a 2-2 draw in the first leg of their Champions League round of 16 tie, leaving the matchup evenly poised heading into the second leg.
